  "title": "Rpm Ep. 54 | Private Equity Discipline in Uncertain Conditions With Lisa Larsson and Akash Chitrey",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>StepStone Group- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2025-12-11T14:03:53+00:00\" title=\"Thursday, December 11, 2025 - 14:03\">Thu, 12/11/2025 - 14:03</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">Rpm Ep. 54 | Private Equity Discipline in Uncertain Conditions With Lisa Larsson and Akash Chitrey</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"IAUM Article (46)\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-12/IAUM%20Article%20%20%2846%29.png\" height=\"422\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-12/IAUM%20Article%20%20%2846%29.png\" width=\"1004\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>In this episode of RPM, Lisa Larsson, a New York-based Partner on StepStone’s Portfolio Management team, and Akash Chitrey, a La Jolla-based Senior Associate on the same team, join co-host Anna Marcus to discuss private equity liquidity and valuations, using data to show how private equity really creates and sustains value, even amid uncertain macro conditions. They cover:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8ccf3b1a861218bba7d9b8eb0d2f8046\">Why liquidity and valuations matter in 2025 (1:07)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9795a20988472f3b093e8e7545983628\">What the data reveals about performance (1:41)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e04d75a25a9c8d5d6aa3106e64f1f415b\">Evolving exit pathways (4:04)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eefcf2fce3c46cdc5503dd6eb0cbcb0d1\">Private equity valuations (8:05)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3737abf585ecaaa044f7ac633e2fe32c\">How private equity creates value (11:45)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9aedd73584ad4d3d35844a357d8a9624\">Discipline in a volatile market (13:48)</li></ul><p>For more on this topic, read our whitepaper “Waiting with conviction: Private equity discipline in uncertain conditions.”</p><p> </p><p></p><p> </p><p>Read the transcript .</p><p>RPM is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, and YouTube—anywhere you normally get your podcasts. Subscribe today!</p><p><a class=\"btn btn-tritory\" href=\"https://insuranceaum.com/stepstone\">READ MORE FROM STEPSTONE GROUP</a></p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.pn